          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Melt and mix",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sift the {{plain-flour}}, {{bicarbonate-of-soda}}, {{ginger-ground}}, {{cinnamon-ground}}, {{mixed-spice}} and {{sea-salt-fine}} into a wide bowl. ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "Melt the {{unsalted-butter}}, {{dark-brown-sugar}} and {{golden-syrup}}",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp99b32a00004cv4asg3l7ku"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " in a small pan over a low heat, stirring, until smooth. Cool for 5 minutes. Pour into the flour, add the beaten {{eggs}}, and mix to a soft dough. Wrap and chill for at least an hour, or overnight.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Roll, cut, bake",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heat the oven to 170°C fan and line two baking trays. Roll the chilled dough on a floured surface to 4 mm thick. Cut shapes with a fluted 7 cm round or shaped cutter, pressing straight down. Lift onto the trays with a palette knife, leaving 2 cm between biscuits. Re-roll the trimmings once. Bake for 10 to 12 minutes; the edges should be deep gold and the centres should be set but still soft. Cool on the tray for 5 minutes (they crisp as they cool), then transfer to a rack.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
